\v 19 r…ôhalah n…ôt…ôl…®gi…ôn tatuv…ôn p…®k o natimnati r…ôha n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni, k…ôni naut…ô m…®ne natimnati t…ôuv…®r m…®n r…ôha n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni kotiuvi r…ôk…®s r…ôhalah n…ôt…ôl…®gi…ôn, motatu-atu e n…®kilah, mol kot…ôp…ôou e noli…ôn n…ôghati…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôni m…ôsot…ôu…ôi…ôn e n…ôualah t…ôuv…®r e n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn r…ôhalah.\x - \xo 4:19  \xt Mat 19:23-24\x*   
