\v 39  \fig ‚Äú!N…®p…ôhri…ôni…ôn, suah u in N…ôt…® Uhg…®n p…ôhri…ôn!‚Äù|alt="Jesus on cross and centurion" src="cn01844B.tif" size="col" loc="Mrk 15:39" copy="Cook" ref="Mak 15:39" \fig* K…ôni i…ôt…ômi asoli r…ôha soldi…ô m…®n i…ôt…ôm t…ômat…ôhtul e n…®kal…® Iesu, t…ômeh m…ôm…ô t…ôm…®m…®s lan…ôha, k…ôni in t…ôm…ôni m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!N…®p…ôhri…ôni…ôn, suah u in N…ôt…® Uhg…®n p…ôhri…ôn!‚Äù   
\p
\v 40 N…®p…ôtan n…ôuvein k…ôm…ôut…ôhtul is…ôu m…ôut…ôsal=pa mauteruh. Ilah n…ôuvein u Meri Makt…ôl…ô, m…®ne iahuni mam…ô r…ôha Jem…®s …ôk…ôku m…®ne Jos…®s, m…®ne S…ôlome.\x - \xo 15:40  \xt Luk 8:2-3\x*  
\v 41 Ilahal k…ôm…ôhl…®t…ôu=p…ôn Iesu nian t…ôm…ôtat…®g Kal…ôli, m…ôhlasiru lan. Ilah n…®p…ôtan tep…ôt k…ômot…ôri m…ôhuv…ôn …ôp…ôha Jerus…®l…ôm ilah Iesu.   
