\v 47 K…ôni Meri Makt…ôl…ô m…®ne Meri mam…ô r…ôha Jos…®s, ilau k…ômueruh ik…®n …ôha k…ôm…ôl…ôhu=p…ôn Iesu ik…®n.   
\c 16  
\s1 Iesu t…®n…ômi…ôg…ôh  //  e r…ôhan n…®m…®si…ôn  
\r (Mat 28:1-8; Luk 24:1-12; Jon 20:1-10)  
\m
\v 1 Nian r…ôha Sap…ôt t…®nuva m…®nuv…ôn r…ôk…®s, k…ôni Meri Makt…ôl…ô m…®ne Meri mam…ô r…ôha Jem…®s, m…®ne S…ôlome k…ômlos n…ôhmt…® nati pien-pien m…®n u n…ômi…ôv…®lah t…ôuv…®r m…ôm…ô ok…®lol=p…ôn e n…®p…ôt…® Iesu.  
